OL,8,FThe broadcast regulator is consulting 
OL,9,Fon changes to the BBC's operating     
OL,10,Flicence. It wants to give the BBC     
OL,11,Fgreater flexibility to make changes to
OL,12,Fits services, removing quotas and the 
OL,13,Fneed to seek Ofcom's approval in some 
OL,14,Finstances.                            
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G1/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35502
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FAt the same time, the BBC wants to    
OL,9,Freplace the BBC News Channel with an  
OL,10,Fad-free simulcast of its international
OL,11,Fservice under the guise of a 'new'    
OL,12,Fservice from April 2023. Removing     
OL,13,Fregulatory conditions will help the BBC
OL,14,Fmake the changes without Ofcom approval
OL,15,Fand without needing a consultation.   
OL,17,FIt's understood this is one of the    
OL,18,Ffactors behind the BBC's decision not 
OL,19,Fto release the full plans to the      
OL,20,Fpublic.                               
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G2/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35503
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FViewers and non-BBC stakeholders have 
OL,9,Fmerely had access to a press release  
OL,10,Fwith selective information about the  
OL,11,Fchanges. Unions within the BBC have had
OL,12,Faccess to greater detail.             
OL,14,FBBC staff are clear about the changes:
OL,15,Fit will mean the current BBC News     
OL,16,FChannel will close.                   
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G3/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35504
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FUnder the proposed new BBC operating  
OL,9,Flicence, Ofcom proposes to remove the 
OL,10,Fcondition on the BBC News channel to  
OL,11,Fprovide more international news, and  
OL,12,Fmore local/regional news than other   
OL,13,Fmain continuous news channels in the  
OL,14,FUK.                                   
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G4/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35505
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FOfcom says: "we do not think that it  
OL,9,Fadds much value to assess the breadth 
OL,10,Fof the BBC's news coverage by comparing
OL,11,Fit to the news coverage of other      
OL,12,Fchannels, as we consider this takes too
OL,13,Fnarrow a view. Instead, we expect to  
OL,14,Fmonitor its performance as we do for  
OL,15,Fother BBC services."                  
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G5/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35506
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FHowever, this condition in the        
OL,9,Foperating licence is the only thing   
OL,10,Fkeeping the remaining UK-specific BBC 
OL,11,FNews Channel hours on air at the      
OL,12,Fmoment. Without the current UK-specific
OL,13,Fdaytime and 8pm news output, the      
OL,14,Fchannel wouldn't be able to provide   
OL,15,F"more local/regional news than other  
OL,16,Fmain continuous news channels in the  
OL,17,FUK."                                  
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G6/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35507
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FWith no conditions attached to the BBC
OL,9,FNews Channel's operating licence, the 
OL,10,FBBC could argue that the remaining    
OL,11,Fsimulcasts of Breakfast and other BBC 
OL,12,FOne news bulletins would continue to  
OL,13,Fensure the channel covers a wide range
OL,14,Fof local and regional news stories    
OL,15,Fafter the changes.                    
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G7/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35508
SC,0008
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FThe BBC has already hollowed out most 
OL,9,Fof the BBC News Channel's off-peak    
OL,10,Fhours in favour of simulcasts. At the 
OL,11,Fmoment, a number of the news simulcasts
OL,12,Fare skewed towards UK news, meaning   
OL,13,Fthey are very different to World News 
OL,14,Fbulletins.                            
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G8/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35509
SC,0009
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FBut BBC staff indicate that this      
OL,9,Fbalance will change in favour of      
OL,10,Finternational stories. That's a       
OL,11,Fcommercial decision, as outside of the
OL,12,FUK, the BBC will want to attract as   
OL,13,Fmany advertisers and broadcast partners
OL,14,Fas possible.                          
OL,16,FWhen reporting on the UK, expect MPs to
OL,17,Fbecome 'lawmakers', the Chancellor of 
OL,18,Fthe Exchequer becomes the 'British    
OL,19,FFinance Minister'. Stories from Leeds,
OL,20,FManchester or Newcastle might reference
OL,21,Fit being 'in the North of England'.   
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                  G9/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35510
SC,0010
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FIn effect, the licence fee payer, who 
OL,9,Fwill be underwriting this commercial  
OL,10,Fenterprise, will see their country    
OL,11,Fbeing reported as if it was a         
OL,12,Fthird-party country.                  
OL,14,FThe BBC justifies the plans due to    
OL,15,Fchanges to the way audiences consume  
OL,16,Fcontent.But the News Channel generates
OL,17,Fa lot of content that is then reused by
OL,18,Fother BBC outlets, including the BBC  
OL,19,FNews website.                         
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
OL,22,                                 G10/11
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
