PN,35511
SC,0011
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F355A1663456596
OL,8,FAnd recent changes to include more    
OL,9,Fnon-UK specific output has helped these
OL,10,Fchanges become a self-fulfilling      
OL,11,Fprophecy as viewers turn over to rival
OL,12,Fbroadcasters for news that's relevant 
OL,13,Fto them.                              
OL,15,FThe consultation on the BBC's operating
OL,16,Flicence runs until 5pm on 14th        
OL,17,FSeptember 2022.                       
OL,3,CViewers have less than a month to     
OL,4,Cpersuade Ofcom not to remove all      
OL,5,Cregulatory conditions relating to the 
OL,6,CBBC News Channel                      
